Recommends: nautilus,
            python3-nautilus,
            python3-gi,
            zenity
Description: minimal Git GUI for Linux with Nautilus integration
 git_view is a Qt 6 application for viewing branch history, working tree
 changes, commits, merges, and remotes. It wraps the system git CLI.
 .
 This package installs:
  * git_view — desktop application and /usr/bin launcher
  * Nautilus Scripts → GitView submenu (works in any file manager session)
  * Nautilus Python extension for TortoiseGit-style context menu items
    when python3-nautilus is installed
 .
 After installation, restart Nautilus: nautilus -q
